Sentece: The samples were extracted with hexane/isoamyl alcohol, separated on a Phenomenex Luna C18 5 mu 150 x 2.1 mm column with a mobile phase consisting of methanol-water-acetic acid (600:400:1) at a flow-rate of 0.3 ml/min.
Title: Determination of fluspirilene in human plasma by liquid chromatography-tandem mass spectrometry with electrospray ionisation.
Name: Fluspirilene

Sentece: The mean recovery for fluspirilene was 90% with a lower limit of quantification of 21.50 pg/ml using 1 ml plasma for extraction.
Title: Determination of fluspirilene in human plasma by liquid chromatography-tandem mass spectrometry with electrospray ionisation.
Name: Fluspirilene
